  "M20.45 20.45h-3.6v-5.45c0-1.3-.02-3-1.82-3-1.82 0-2.1 1.42-2.1 2.9v5.55h-3.6V9h3.46v1.56h.05a3.8 3.8 0 0 1 3.42-1.88c3.66 0 4.34 2.4 4.34 5.5v6.82zM5.34 7.43a2.1 2.1 0 1 1 0-4.2 2.1 2.1 0 0 1 0 4.2zM7.14 20.45H3.52V9h3.62v11.45zM22.23 0H1.77C.8 0 0 .77 0 1.72v20.56C0 23.23.8 24 1.77 24h20.46c.97 0 1.77-.77 1.77-1.72V1.72c0-.95-.8-1.72-1.77-1.72z";
